acceptance_criteria: "isPathWithinDirectory comparison uses consistently canonicalized source AND destination when the destination parent does not exist, on symlinked (macOS) and short-name (Windows) temp paths; extension-copy-safety.spec.ts passes on all 5 nightly legs; regression coverage pins the nonexistent-destination-parent + symlinked-tmpdir case"
parent: pm-ugqx
risk: medium
confidence: high
resolution: Canonicalize each destination ancestor from the filesystem root before containment checks and stage nested copies safely.
expected_result: Extension installation succeeds through symlinked macOS temp roots and Windows alternate path namespaces.
actual_result: Missing-parent symlink regression and all cross-platform contract tests pass.
